  "prompt": "Kindly suggest the best NPTE classes in NY?",
  "response": "Here are some well-regarded NPTE (National Physical Therapy Exam) preparation classes in New York:\n\n1. **APTA (American Physical Therapy Association)** - While not a traditional class, they often provide resources, study guides, and workshops that can be beneficial for NPTE preparation.\n\n2. **Kaplan** - Known for comprehensive test prep, Kaplan offers a variety of NPTE review courses, including live lectures, online resources, and practice exams.\n\n3. **Elite Physical Therapy Exam Review** - Offers NPTE review courses with experienced instructors and a focus on high-yield topics, workshops, and practice questions.\n\n4. **PT Final Exam** - They provide comprehensive review courses and resources specifically tailored for NPTE candidates, including live classes and online resources.\n\n5. **Scorebuilders** - They offer in-depth review courses that include lecture materials, practice questions, and mock exams tailored for the NPTE.\n\n6. **TherapyExamPrep.com** - Online format with a variety of resources, including video lectures, practice questions, and study materials catering to NPTE exam preparation.\n\n7. **PhysioU** - Offers NPTE review courses and resources, including online workshops and study guides aimed at helping students prepare effectively.\n\nBefore enrolling, it's a good idea to check their specific offerings, schedules, and formats (online or in-person) to find the one that best fits your learning style and needs. Additionally, reading reviews and testimonials from past students can also provide insight into the effectiveness of the classes.",
